00:32:56.785 --> 00:32:58.265
¿Quieres tener uno?

00:32:58.545 --> 00:32:59.225
Claro.

00:33:03.465 --> 00:33:04.146
Es delicioso.

00:33:05.745 --> 00:33:06.826
Entonces me iré a casa primero.

00:33:06.866 --> 00:33:07.505
Peilan.

00:33:07.906 --> 00:33:08.985
